&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic oversight across campaign planning, activation, optimization, budget allocation, and measurement to drive strong business outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate campaign performance data and market insights into actionable recommendations, strategic narratives, and executive-level presentations for clients and internal stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities for innovation, testing, audience expansion, and channel growth across client programs&lt;/li&gt;
