&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Data Scientist you will play a key role in ensuring high-quality data delivery, improving reporting frameworks, and supporting deeper analysis to inform internal decision-making. This role builds on strong data foundations and introduces more advanced analytical thinking, while maintaining a focus on scalable execution and operational excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with internal and cross-functional teams to enhance data processes, support performance analysis, and contribute to more efficient and data-driven decision-making across accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Revamp an existing customer lead scoring model predicting conversion propensity based on web behavior across regional brand websites. Address current data lag and interpretability issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a strategic partner to the client&#39;s digital analytics team, taking conceptual questions and pitching &quot;white space&quot; mathematical/statistical opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build/run models to support client Marketing Mix Modeling readouts. Leverage 1PD and third-party data (TransUnion) to uncover insights, perform clustering, and develop predictive targeting segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help trial and evaluate new platforms (proprietary and 3rd party) for built-in AI capabilities and enhancements over existing reporting and analytical tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must Have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8-10 years of professional and practical experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of applied statistics and testing methodologies, preferably within the media analytics space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of Python, SQL and Machine Learning algorithms (Classification, Regression, Clustering, XGBoost Library).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be comfortable navigating and extracting data from AWS environments (e.g. Athena), Adobe Analytics, Google Analytics, Knime, and Dashboards (Tableau).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced english level (B2+/C1) is a strict and mandatory requirement.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marketing Mix Modeling (MMM), audience segmentation, and model interpretability (e.g., SHAP/LIME).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
