&lt;p&gt;About Kepler:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kepler is the agency for today’s most ambitious brands -- a leading omnichannel, full-funnel, full-service agency, powered by the proprietary Kip platform, specializing in media, creative, data, and technology. We are at the forefront of marketing innovation, helping our clients navigate the ever-evolving landscape of consumer behavior, culture, and AI. Kepler is seeking a visionary leader to explore and push the boundaries of what great looks like in Paid Social Media.&lt;/p&gt;
